transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thanks for calling Viagra, this is Charles.

Speaker 2: Charles, this is Dave Christensen calling.

Speaker 1: I somehow got hooked up on a prescription set up

Speaker 2: with you guys that I did not authorize.

Speaker 1: I had called about three months ago, canceled it,

Speaker 2: and they said, OK, you're taken care of.

Speaker 1: And I've had two shipments since.

Speaker 2: And I want it stopped.

Speaker 1: Gotcha.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I don't know why it started it back up.

Speaker 1: You didn't try to order, did you?

Speaker 2: Nope.

Speaker 1: Gotcha.

Speaker 2: OK.

Speaker 1: I just stopped everything right now.

Speaker 2: I do see all the notes and everything like that.

Speaker 1: I don't know what happened.

Speaker 2: If you want a refund for that last one,

Speaker 1: there's a Southgate, Kentucky address on the pill bottle.

Speaker 2: Send it back to us, and we'll issue the refund

Speaker 1: for that last one, OK?

Speaker 2: OK, thank you.

Speaker 1: Yes, sir.

Speaker 2: Bye-bye.

Speaker 1: Bye.
